    <category>
      <pattern>MORE UNIVERSAL CREDIT HELP</pattern>
      <template>
        To apply for universal credit, there are a few conditions which will be listed below:
        - You must live in the UK.
        - You must be older than 18 years old, but there are however a couple of exceptions.
        - You must be under the state pension age.
        - You must have £16,000 or less in money, savings and investments.
        - You may make claims for support depending on health conditions or disabilities. To find out more regarding disabilities, please follow this link: https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-disability-universal-credit.
        - For under 18s, there are a few other conditions that apply, if you would like to know please specify below.
      </template>
    </category>

